<H3> <TI>   Hamas Claims Responsibility for 'Afula Attack </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Hamas Claims Responsibility for 'Afula Attack </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   TA0604151094 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 1400 GMT 6 Apr 
94 </F>

<F P=103> TA0604151094 </F>
<F P=104>  Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el </F>
<F P=105>  Hebrew </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Hamas [Islamic Resistance Movement] has assumed 
responsibility for the 'Afula attack, claiming that its men 
perpetrated the attack. In a leaflet distributed in Janin, 
Hamas said that the name of the suicide terrorist is Ra'id 
Zakarnah, 19, of Qabatiyah. 
  Our correspondent Moti Amir reports that a short while ago, 
the security forces arrived in Qabatiyah, and took Zakarnah's 
father to the Ha'emeq Hospital to identify the body. 

</TEXT>

