<H3> <TI>   Update on `Terrorist' Attack </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Update on `Terrorist' Attack </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   TA0704065294 Tel Aviv IDF Radio in Hebrew 0630 GMT 7 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> TA0704065294 </F>
<F P=104>  Tel Aviv IDF Radio </F>
<F P=105>  Hebrew </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Here is an updated report on the terrorist attack 
at the Ashdod Junction: At least four Israelis were wounded in 
this attack. Two people were seriously wounded, while another 
two sustained moderate injuries. The wounded were taken to 
Rehovot's Kaplan Hospital where the hospital director later told 
us that one of the casualties had died of his wounds. The 
nationality of the dead man remains unknown. 
  One of the terrorists was killed, but his accomplice or 
accomplices managed to escape. According to the reports, the 
terrorists fired from a bus or car at people standing at a 
hitchhiking stop at the Ashdod Junction. The dead terrorist was 
killed by bystanders who shot at him from the junction. 

</TEXT>

