<H3> <TI>   YSP Official Said Killed in Ta'izz Governorate </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    YSP Official Said Killed in Ta'izz Governorate </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   JN0604125994 Paris Radio Monte Carlo in Arabic 1200 GMT 6 
Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> JN0604125994 </F>
<F P=104>  Paris Radio Monte Carlo </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Yemeni Socialist Party [YSP] sources announced 
today that Ahmad Khalid Sayf, the secretary of the YSP branch in 
al-Najdah region in the Ta'izz Governorate was killed there, 
where the Yemeni Government is scheduled to convene today. The 
deceased's body, according to the sources, was found last Monday 
[4 April] evening close to the general reserve camp. 
Eyewitnesses report that Sayf was shot by unknown gunmen, who 
fled the scene in a getaway car. 

</TEXT>

