  To another question, the spokesman said the entire spectrum 
of Pakistan-U.S. relations would come under review during the 
three-day visit of the U.S. deputy secretary of state, Mr. 
Strobe Talbott, beginning from Friday [8 April]. The spokesman 
said the agenda of talks is very broad and we are prepared to 
