<H3> <TI>   Wrapup of Reports on Arafat Messages, Meetings </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Wrapup of Reports on Arafat Messages, Meetings </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    Yeltsin Updated on Peace Process </H4>

<F P=102> LD0704182594 Algiers Voice of Palestine in Arabic 1702 GMT 7 
Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0704182594 </F>
<F P=104>  Algiers Voice of Palestine </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Brother Abu-'Ammar [Yasir 'Arafat], president of the 
state of Palestine and chairman of the PLO Executive Committee, 
received his excellency the Russian ambassador in Cairo this 
afternoon. The brother president entrusted the Russian 
ambassador with a message for President Boris Yeltsin on the 
latest developments in the peace negotiations and the obstacles 
the Israeli Government is producing to hinder the implementation 
of the declaration of principles accord, signed in Washington, 
and the agreements signed in Cairo, a matter which exposes the 
peace process to danger. 

</TEXT>

