<H3> <TI>   `Terrorist,' Soldier Killed in Shoot-Out 7 Apr </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    `Terrorist,' Soldier Killed in Shoot-Out 7 Apr </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   NC0704203494 Cairo MENA in Arabic 1950 GMT 7 Apr 94 </F>
