<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] At 1230 today, His Excellency President Hafiz 
al-Asad received Hojjat ol-Eslam Hasan Ruhani, Iranian deputy 
Majles speaker and chairman of the Majles Foreign Relations 
Committee, and the delegation accompanying him. 
