<H4>    Meets With Buwayz </H4>

<F P=102> NC0604183194 Beirut Radio Lebanon in Arabic 1530 GMT 6 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC0604183194 </F>
<F P=104>  Beirut Radio Lebanon </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Spanish Foreign Minister Javier Solana arrived in 
Beirut from Cairo on a 24-hour visit to Lebanon during which he 
will meet the three leaders and hold talks with his counterpart 
Faris Buwayz. Immediately upon arrival, the Spanish minister 
headed for the Foreign Ministry, where he met Minister Buwayz. 

</TEXT>

