<F P=100> SYRIA </F>
<H3> <TI>   Al-Asad, Khaddam Meet Iranian Parliamentary Delegation </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Al-Asad, Khaddam Meet Iranian Parliamentary Delegation </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   JN0704140394 Damascus Syrian Arab Republic Radio Network in 
Arabic 1115 GMT 7 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> JN0704140394 </F>
<F P=104>  Damascus Syrian Arab Republic Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] At 1230 today, His Excellency President Hafiz 
al-Asad received Hojjat ol-Eslam Hasan Ruhani, Iranian deputy 
Majles speaker and chairman of the Majles Foreign Relations 
Committee, and the delegation accompanying him. 
  The meeting was attended by Dr. 'Adil Jamus, deputy speaker 
of the People's Assembly; Shakir Is'ayyid, chairman of the Arab 
and Foreign Relations Committee of the People's Assembly; and 
Iranian Ambassador in Damascus Mohammad Hasan Akhtari-Foruqi. 
  Also at 0930 today, Vice President 'Abd-a-Halim Khaddam 
received Hojjat ol-Eslam Hasan Ruhani and his delegation. The 
meeting was attended by 'Adil Jamus, Shakir Is'ayyid, and 
Mohammad Hasan Akhtari-Foruqi. 
  The talks dealt with the situation in the region, the latest 
developments in the Arab-Israeli conflict, the international 
state of affairs, and bilateral ties. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

