<H3> <TI>   Foreign Minister Confers With PLO Officials </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Foreign Minister Confers With PLO Officials </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   NC0904203694 Cairo MENA in Arabic 2025 GMT 9 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC0904203694 </F>
<F P=104>  Cairo MENA </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Cairo, 9 Apr (MENA)--Foreign Minister 'Amr Musa 
tonight met Mahmud 'Abbas, member of the PLO Executive 
Committee; Sa'id Kamal, Palestinian Ambassador to Cairo; and 
Zuhdi al-Qidrah, representative of the Fatah Movement in Cairo. 
