officials reviewed current developments related to the 
Palestinian issue and the tension in the occupied territories. 
Matters concerning the resumption of Palestinian-Israeli talks 
in Cairo tomorrow, Sunday, and the obstacles facing the 
formulation of a timetable for the withdrawal of Israeli forces 
from Gaza and Jericho were also discussed. 

