<H3> <TI>   Army Command Urges University Graduates To Enlist </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Army Command Urges University Graduates To Enlist </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   NC0904190194 Cairo MENA in Arabic 1845 GMT 9 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC0904190194 </F>
<F P=104>  Cairo MENA </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Khartoum, 9 Apr (MENA)--The Sudanese Armed Forces 
General Command today called on all graduates of universities, 
higher institutes, and high schools to quickly join the national 
service by joining the ranks of the armed forces. It warned 
that if the graduates fail to join the Armed Forces, they will 
be subject to punishment according to the law. 

</TEXT>

