<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Roundup of Security Activities, Conflicts in South </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    Missiles, Arms Seized Near LF Center </H4>

<F P=102> NC0204194694 Beirut Radio Lebanon in Arabic 1900 GMT 2 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC0204194694 </F>
<F P=104>  Beirut Radio Lebanon </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The Army continues its raids and searches for arms 
caches and ammunition. This morning it discovered one arms 
cache in Fatqa and another one in Ghidras that is only around 
200 meters from the former headquarters of the Lebanese Forces 
[LF]. A large quantity of weapons, ammunitions, and war 
material were confiscated, which filled four trucks and included 
640 rifles of various types, 40 antiaircraft missiles, and a 
military radio transmitter in addition to various types of 
spares parts, weapons, and ammunition. 

</TEXT>

