<F P=100> JORDAN </F>
<H3> <TI>   Yemeni Education Minister al-Qirbi Visits </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Yemeni Education Minister al-Qirbi Visits </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    Arrives With Letter for al-Majali </H4>

<F P=102> JN0804163094 Amman Radio Jordan in English 1600 GMT 8 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> JN0804163094 </F>
<F P=104>  Amman Radio Jordan </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


