<F P=106> ["Exclusive" report] </F>
  [Text] Mas'ud Rajavi, leader of the Iranian resistance, has 
urged the Iranian people to escalate the struggle against the 
ruling regime in Iran, to pave the way for the liberation army 
to pounce on the regime. 
  Addressing the sons of Iran during a gathering of thousands 
of national liberation army fighters at one of the liberation 
army's camps [in Iraq] on the new Iranian year, Rajavi said: 
