will pave the way for the liberation army's major assault. The 
regime is destined to fall." 
  The resistance leader gave an elaborate account of the 
Iranians' tragic economic and social situation under the ruling 
regime because of the $50-million foreign debt and the collapse 
of the rial exchange rate. 

