<H3> <TI>   'Arafat Adviser Reponds to Peres' Afula Remarks </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    'Arafat Adviser Reponds to Peres' Afula Remarks </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1004080194 Algiers Voice of Palestine in Arabic 1702 GMT 9 
