<H4>    Talks Resume in Cairo </H4>

<F P=102> NC1004112194 Cairo Arab Republic of Egypt Radio Network in 
Arabic 1100 GMT 10 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> NC1004112194 </F>
<F P=104>  Cairo Arab Republic of Egypt Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Palestinian-Israeli talks on ratifying the 
Gaza-Jericho agreement resumed in Cairo today. 
  The Palestinian side was chaired by Dr. Nabil Sha'th, 
Palestinian President Yasir 'Arafat's political adviser, and the 
Israeli side was chaired by General Amnon Shahaq, who arrived in 
Cairo earlier today. 

</TEXT>

