<F P=102> NC1104103494 Cairo MENA in Arabic 0947 GMT 11 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC1104103494 </F>
<F P=104>  Cairo MENA </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Cairo, 11 Apr (MENA)--The Palestinian-Israeli 
negotiations on the implementation of the Gaza-Jericho agreement 
resumed here again today. The Palestinian delegation to the 
negotiations is being led by Dr. Nabil Sha'th, Palestinian 
president Yasir 'Arafat's political adviser, and the Israeli 
delegation by Amnon Shahaq, deputy Israeli chief of staff. 
  The Security, Civilian, and Legal Affairs Committees are 
meeting during this round of negotiations. 

</TEXT>

