BFN 

  [Text] The speaker of Iranian parliament, Hojjat Ol-Eslam 
Nateq-Nuri, has castigated the atrocities being perpetrated on 
Muslims in occupied Kashmir, Bosnia-Herzegovina, and Palestine 
during a call on Prime Minister Benazir Bhutto in Islamabad 
