Alois Mock, the foreign minister, and (Erik Fetman), deputy 
minister of public economy and transport. 
  President Hafiz al-Asad and President Klestil held a meeting 
at Tishrin Palace. The meeting was attended on the Austrian 
side by members of the accompanying delegation and on the Syrian 
side by Vice Presidents 'Abd-al-Halim Khaddam and Dr. Muhammad 
Zuhayr Mashariqah, Prime Minister Mahmud al-Zu'bi, and Foreign 
Minister Faruq al-Shar'. 

