<H3> <TI>   Austrian President Klestil, Delegation Visit </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Austrian President Klestil, Delegation Visit </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    Klestil Receives Khaddam </H4>

<F P=102> JN1004185494 Damascus Syrian Arab Television Network in 
Arabic 1730 GMT 10 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> JN1004185494 </F>
<F P=104>  Damascus Syrian Arab Television Network </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] At 1900 today, Austrian President Thomas Klestil 
received at his residence Vice President 'Abd-al-Halim Khaddam. 
Talks dealt with the past phases of the peace process, the 
international situation, and bilateral relations. 

</TEXT>

