<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Deputy Foreign Minister Yosi Beilin, who will be 
departing for Oman this weekend, says that this visit is a big 
leap forward as far as the Arab boycott is concerned. According 
to him, Oman is hosting the multilateral talks on water affairs 
because it wants to solve its water problems, and Israel can 
offer it know-how and joint research projects. Beilin was 
